s%20were%20delayed%2C%20while%20six%20Delhi-bound%20flights%20were%20diverted.%20On%20Friday%2C%20more%20than%20400%20flights%20were%20delayed%20due%20to%20bad%20weather%20conditions%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20CAT%20III%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT%20III%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fskybrary.aero%2Farticles%2Finstrument-landing-system-ils%5C%22%3EInstrument%20Landing%20System%20(ILS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20aids%20planes%20in%20landing%20in%20extremely%20poor%20visibility%20conditions%2C%20providing%20pilots%20ground-based%20radio%20navigation%20about%20the%20aircraft's%20runway%20alignment%20and%20glide%20path.%20The%20system%20employs%20two%20radio%20beams%20that%20offer%20horizontal%20and%20vertical%20assistance%20during%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aai.aero%2Fen%2Fcontent%2Fwhat-are-different-facility-performance-categories-operation-ils%5C%22%3ECAT%20III%20A%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20permits%20landing%20of%20aircraft%20upto%20Runway%20Visual%20Range%20(RVR)%20not%20less%20than%20200%20meters.%20CAT%20III%20B%20permits%20landing%20of%20aircraft%20when%20RVR%20is%20less%20than%20200%C2%A0meters%20but%20not%20less%20than%2050%20meters%2C%20while%20CAT%20III%20C%20allows%20landing%20in%20zero%20visibility%20conditions.%20These%20conditions%20include%20those%20arising%20out%20of%20snow%2C%20rain%2C%20or%20in%20Delhi's%20case%2C%20fog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-fog-delhi-smog-delhi-pollution-how-to-drive-safely-in-dense-fog-smog-here-are-5-driving-tips-7388729%5C%22%3EUnsure%20How%20To%20Drive%20Safely%20In%20Fog%3F%20Here%20Are%20Our%205%20Tips%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20horizontal%20and%20vertical%20guidance%2C%20CAT%20III%20also%20provides%20data%20on%20approach%20trajectory%20and%20touchdown%20zone.%20Further%2C%20guidance%20is%20also%20given%20regarding%20the%20distance%20left%20to%20the%20runway%2C%20when%20to%20deploy%20flaps%20and%20apply%20brakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAT%20II%20system%20guides%20the%20aircraft%20in%20the%20event%20that%20the%20RVR%20is%20not%20less%20than%20350%20metres%2C%20while%20a%20CAT%20I%20system%20assists%20landing%20for%20a%20RVR%20of%20over%20550%20metres.%20The%20RVR%20is%20the%20distance%20till%20which%20the%20pilot%20can%20see%20the%20runway's%20lights%20or%20markers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20Indian%20Airports%20Are%20CAT%20III%20Compliant%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20six%20airports%20in%20India%20where%20the%20runways%20are%20certified%20for%20CAT%20III%20B%20operations%20-%20Delhi%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT%20III%20A%20system%20was%20first%20installed%20on%20runway%2028%20at%20Delhi's%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20airport%20in%20year%202001%20and%20was%20upgraded%20to%20CAT%20III%20B%20ILS%20with%20Advanced%20Surface%20Movement%20Guidance%20and%20Control%20Systems%20(ASMGCS)%20in%202005%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2055%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20an%20airport%20runway%20being%20compliant%20to%20a%20CAT%20category%2C%20landing%20under%20the%20said%20category%20is%20also%20dependent%20on%20flight%20equipment%20and%20pilot%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20Indian%20airport%20is%20CAT%20III%20C%20complaint%20yet.%20The%20system%20is%20in%20application%20at%20New%20York's%20John%20F%20Kennedy%20International%20Airport%20and%20London's%20Heathrow%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735958880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fqu0dil2o_dehi-airport_625x300_03_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-as-delhi-witnesses-dense-fog-how-flights-land-safely-in-zero-visibility-conditions-7395949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20is%20witnessing%20dense%20fog%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20day%20on%20Saturday%2C%20prompting%20the%20airport%20to%20state%20in%20an%20advisory%20that%20flights%20that%20are%20not%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20might%20get%20affected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20Says%20Trump%20To%20Be%20Sentenced%20In%20Hush%20Money%20Case%20On%20January%2010%2C%20He%20Reacts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20judge%20presiding%20over%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20hush%20money%20case%20on%20Friday%20set%20sentencing%20for%2010%20days%20before%20his%20January%2020%20inauguration%20and%20said%20he%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20impose%20jail%20time.%20Judge%20Juan%20Merchan%20said%20Trump%2C%20the%20first%20former%20president%20ever%20convicted%20of%20a%20crime%2C%20can%20appear%20either%20in%20person%20or%20virtually%20at%20his%20January%2010%20sentencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%2018-page%20decision%2C%20Merchan%20upheld%20Trump's%20conviction%20by%20a%20New%20York%20jury%2C%20rejecting%20various%20motions%20from%20Trump's%20lawyers%20seeking%20to%20have%20it%20thrown%20out.%20The%20judge%20said%20that%20instead%20of%20incarceration%20he%20was%20leaning%20towards%20an%20unconditional%20discharge%20--%20meaning%20the%20real%20estate%20tycoon%20would%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20any%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sentence%20would%20nevertheless%20see%20Trump%20entering%20the%20White%20House%20as%20a%20convicted%20felon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2078-year-old%20Trump%20potentially%20faced%20up%20to%20four%20years%20in%20prison%20but%20legal%20experts%20--%20even%20before%20he%20won%20the%20November%20presidential%20election%20--%20did%20not%20expect%20Merchan%20to%20send%20the%20former%20president%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20proper%20at%20this%20juncture%20to%20make%20known%20the%20Court's%20inclination%20to%20not%20impose%20any%20sentence%20of%20incarceration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20prosecutors%20also%20did%20not%20believe%20a%20jail%20term%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpracticable%20recommendation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20lodge%20an%20appeal%20that%20could%20potentially%20delay%20his%20sentencing%2C%20denounced%20the%20decision%20late%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20illegitimate%20political%20attack%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20Rigged%20Charade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20his%20platform%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Merchan%20a%20%26quot%3Bradical%20partisan%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added%20that%20the%20order%20was%20%26quot%3Bknowingly%20unlawful%2C%20goes%20against%20our%20Constitution%20and%2C%20if%20allowed%20to%20stand%2C%20would%20be%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Presidency%20as%20we%20know%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20convicted%20in%20New%20York%20in%20May%20of%2034%20counts%20of%20falsifying%20business%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20hush%20money%20payment%20to%20porn%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%202016%20election%20to%20stop%20her%20from%20revealing%20an%20alleged%202006%20sexual%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20attorneys%20had%20sought%20to%20have%20the%20case%20dismissed%20on%20multiple%20grounds%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20landmark%20ruling%20last%20year%20that%20former%20US%20presidents%20have%20sweeping%20immunity%20from%20prosecution%20for%20a%20range%20of%20official%20acts%20committed%20while%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerchan%20rejected%20that%20argument%20but%20he%20noted%20that%20Trump%20will%20be%20immune%20from%20prosecution%20once%20he%20is%20sworn%20in%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFinding%20no%20legal%20impediment%20to%20sentencing%20and%20recognizing%20that%20Presidential%20immunity%20will%20likely%20attach%20once%20Defendant%20takes%20his%20Oath%20of%20Office%2C%20it%20is%20incumbent%20upon%20this%20Court%20to%20set%20this%20matter%20down%20for%20imposition%20of%20sentence%20prior%20to%20January%2020%2C%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Witch%20Hunts'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20spokesperson%20Steven%20Cheung%20denounced%20Merchan's%20decision%20to%20set%20sentencing%20for%20the%20former%20president%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Immunity%20decision%20and%20other%20longstanding%20jurisprudence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20lawless%20case%20should%20have%20never%20been%20brought%20and%20the%20Constitution%20demands%20that%20it%20be%20immediately%20dismissed%2C%26quot%3B%20Cheung%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20must%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20the%20Presidential%20Transition%20process%20and%20to%20execute%20the%20vital%20duties%20of%20the%20presidency%2C%20unobstructed%20by%20the%20remains%20of%20this%20or%20any%20remnants%20of%20the%20Witch%20Hunts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20no%20sentencing%2C%20and%20President%20Trump%20will%20continue%20fighting%20against%20these%20hoaxes%20until%20they%20are%20all%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Cheung%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20faced%20two%20federal%20cases%20brought%20by%20special%20counsel%20Jack%20Smith%20but%20both%20were%20dropped%20under%20a%20long-standing%20Justice%20Department%20policy%20of%20not%20prosecuting%20a%20sitting%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20cases%2C%20Trump%20was%20accused%20of%20conspiring%20to%20overturn%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%20he%20lost%20to%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20removing%20large%20quantities%20of%20top%20secret%20documents%20after%20leaving%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20faces%20racketeering%20charges%20in%20Georgia%20over%20his%20alleged%20efforts%20to%20subver