3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20British%20government%20minister%20on%20Friday%20criticised%20Elon%20Musk's%20latest%20intervention%20in%20the%20country's%20politics%20as%20%26quot%3Bmisjudged%20and%20certainly%20misinformed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20billionaire%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20a%20day%20earlier%20of%20failing%20to%20bring%20%26quot%3Brape%20gangs%26quot%3B%20to%20justice%20when%20he%20was%20director%20of%20public%20prosecutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20string%20of%20posts%20on%20his%20X%20platform%2C%20Musk%20also%20suggested%20that%20Jess%20Phillips%2C%20minister%20for%20the%20prevention%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20%26quot%3Bdeserves%20to%20be%20in%20prison%26quot%3B%20for%20refusing%20a%20request%20for%20a%20national%20public%20inquiry%20into%20a%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20scandal%20in%20the%20northern%20English%20city%20of%20Oldham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Secretary%20Wes%20Streeting%20told%20ITV%20News%20television%20that%20Musk's%20comments%20were%20wide%20of%20the%20mark%20and%20that%20the%20government%20took%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20seriously%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20criticisms%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20made%2C%20I%20think%20are%20misjudged%20and%20certainly%20misinformed%2C%20but%20we're%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20I%20think%20has%20got%20a%20big%20role%20to%20play%20with%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20to%20help%20us%20and%20other%20countries%20to%20tackle%20this%20serious%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20work%20with%20us%20and%20roll%20his%20sleeves%20up%2C%20we'd%20welcome%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20widespread%20abuse%20of%20girls%20in%20a%20number%20of%20English%20towns%20and%20cities%20including%20Rochdale%2C%20Rotherham%20and%20Oldham%2C%20which%20emerged%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20has%20long%20stirred%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20court%20cases%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20convictions%20of%20dozens%20of%20men%2C%20mostly%20of%20South%20Asian%20Muslim%20origin.%20The%20victims%20were%20vulnerable%2C%20mostly%20white%2C%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20official%20inquiries%20into%20how%20police%20and%20social%20workers%20failed%20to%20halt%20the%20abuse%20found%20that%20officials%20in%20some%20cases%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20avoid%20appearing%20racist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scandals%20have%20been%20seized%20upon%20by%20far-right%20figures%2C%20in%20particular%20Tommy%20Robinson%2C%20a%20prominent%20extremist%20agitator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccused%20of%20helping%20fuel%20anti-immigration%20riots%20last%20summer%2C%20Robinson%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20October%20after%20he%20admitted%20committing%20contempt%20of%20court%20over%20a%20long-running%20libel%20case%20involving%20a%20Syrian%20refugee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20his%20X%20posts%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Musk%20claimed%20that%20Robinson%20was%20in%20prison%20%26quot%3Bfor%20telling%20the%20truth%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20should%20be%20freed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Swipe%20at%20Starmer%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Musk's%20messages%20focused%20on%20Robinson's%20long-time%20highlighting%20of%20historical%20scandals%20involving%20alleged%20paedophile%20grooming%20gangs%20in%20some%20English%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20various%20other%20accounts'%20claims%20around%20the%20child%20sex%20crimes%20spanning%20decades%2C%20Musk%20noted%20that%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS)%20decides%20whether%20to%20charge%20suspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20was%20the%20head%20of%20the%20CPS%20when%20rape%20gangs%20were%20allowed%20to%20exploit%20young%20girls%20without%20facing%20justice%3F%20Keir%20Starmer%2C%202008-2013%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20was%20the%20head%20of%20the%20CPS%20in%20that%20period%2C%20but%20none%20of%20the%20probes%20into%20the%20scandals%20singled%20him%20out%20for%20blame%20or%20found%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20block%20prosecutions%20due%20to%20concerns%20over%20alleged%20Islamophobia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20response%20to%20another%20post%20calling%20for%20King%20Charles%20III%20to%20dissolve%20parliament%2C%20Musk%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYes!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20took%20another%20swipe%20at%20Starmer%2C%20suggesting%20that%20his%20government%20had%20turned%20down%20the%20requested%20inquiry%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20he%20is%20guilty%20of%20complicity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeighing%20in%20on%20the%20row%2C%20later%20on%20Friday%20Nigel%20Farage%2C%20a%20lawmaker%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20anti-immigration%20Reform%20UK%20party%2C%20disagreed%20with%20Musk%20about%20Robinson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20sees%20Robinson%20as%20one%20of%20these%20people%20that%20fought%20against%20the%20grooming%20gangs.%20But%20of%20course%20the%20truth%20is%20Tommy%20Robinson's%20in%20prison%20not%20for%20that%2C%20but%20for%20contempt%20of%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20right-wing%20channel%20GB%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobinson%20himself%20had%20encouraged%20a%20narrative%20that%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20prisoner...%20but%20it%20isn't%20quite%20true%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarage%20added%20that%20Musk%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20had%20talks%20about%20the%20US%20billionaire%20donating%20to%20his%20hard-right%20party%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20supportive%20of%20me%2C%20he's%20very%20supportive%20of%20the%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735935960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%