nsitive%20issue%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20said%20it%20will%20devise%20an%20effective%20mechanism%20to%20combat%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20educational%20institutions%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20directed%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20to%20notify%20draft%20regulations%20to%20ensure%20no%20caste-based%20discrimination%20happened%20with%20students%20in%20the%20central%2C%20state%2C%20private%20and%20deemed%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20directed%20the%20UGC%20to%20furnish%20data%20on%20the%20number%20of%20institutions%20which%20had%20established%20equal%20opportunity%20cells%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20UGC%20(Promotion%20of%20Equity%20in%20Higher%20Educational%20Institutions%20Regulations)%202012%2C%20popularly%20called%20%26quot%3BUGC%20equity%20regulations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20equally%20conscious%20of%20this%20sensitive%20issue.%20We%20will%20do%20something.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20find%20out%20some%20effective%20mechanism%20and%20modalities%20to%20see%20that%20the%202012%20regulations%20are%20translated%20into%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sought%20Centre's%20response%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20asked%20the%20UGC%20to%20furnish%20data%20within%20six%20weeks%20on%20the%20complaints%20over%20such%20discrimination%20among%20students%20in%20all%20universities%20and%20higher%20education%20institutions%20besides%20the%20consequent%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Indira%20Jaising%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20mothers%20of%20students%20Rohith%20Vemula%20and%20Payal%20Tadvi%2C%20who%20allegedly%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20facing%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20said%20from%202004%20till%20now%20over%2050%20students%20(mostly%20from%20SC%2FST)%20had%20killed%20themselves%20in%20IITs%20and%20other%20institutions%20after%20facing%20such%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vemula%2C%20a%20PhD%20scholar%20at%20Hyderabad%20Central%20University%20died%20on%20January%2017%2C%202016%2C%20Tadvi%2C%20a%20student%20at%20TN%20Topiwala%20National%20Medical%20College%2C%20died%20on%20May%2022%2C%202019%2C%20after%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20purported%20discrimination%20by%20three%20doctors%20in%20her%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20a%20PIL%20was%20filed%20in%202019%20but%20no%20substantial%20hearing%20had%20taken%20place%20on%20the%20issue%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20now%20on%20we%20will%20list%20this%20petition%20periodically%20so%20that%20some%20effective%20solution%20could%20be%20found%20in%20the%20matter%20as%20since%202019%20nothing%20much%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%20counsel%20submitted%20a%20committee%20constituted%20by%20it%20gave%20recommendation%20and%20the%20commission%20drafted%20new%20regulations%20to%20stop%20caste-based%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20draft%20regulations%20need%20to%20be%20put%20on%20the%20website%20to%20invite%20objections%20and%20suggestions%20from%20the%20public%20in%20a%20month's%20time%20and%20thereafter%20it%20will%20be%20notified%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20questioned%20the%20UGC%20over%20the%20delay%20and%20said%20it%20had%20been%20sleeping%20all%20this%20while%20and%20not%20come%20up%20with%20new%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20time%20is%20needed%20to%20notify%20the%20new%20regulations%3F%20You%20do%20it%20in%20one%20month%20and%20place%20it%20on%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20after%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sought%20the%20assistance%20of%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20on%20the%20matter%20along%20with%20the%20response%20of%20the%20National%20Assessment%20and%20Accreditation%20Council%2C%20an%20autonomous%20institution%20under%20the%20UGC%20which%20assesses%20and%20accredits%20higher%20education%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2020%2C%202019%2C%20the%20top%20court%20issued%20notice%20on%20the%20PIL%20which%20also%20sought%20to%20enforce%20the%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20particularly%20the%20Right%20to%20Equality%2C%20Right%20to%20Prohibition%20of%20Discrimination%20against%20caste%2C%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20alleged%20%26quot%3Brampant%20prevalence%26quot%3B%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20throughout%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20UGC%20to%20strictly%20ensure%20the%20enforcement%20and%20compliance%20of%20the%202012%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20directions%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20UGC%2C%20the%20plea%20asked%20to%20ensure%20all%20the%20educational%20institutions%2C%20complied%20with%20the%20regulations%20in%20%26quot%3Bletter%20and%20in%20spirit%26quot%3B%20apart%20from%20establishing%20equal%20opportunity%20cells%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20similarly%20existing%20anti-discrimination%20internal%20complaints%20mechanisms%2C%20and%20have%20representation%20from%20the%20SC%2FST%2C%20NGOs%20or%20social%20sector%20to%20ensure%20objectivity%20and%20impartiality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20a%20direction%20was%20sought%20to%20all%20universities%20to%20take%20strong%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20victimisation%20of%20students%20or%20staff%20over%20caste-based%20discrimination%20and%20protecting%20students%20from%20any%20hostility%20in%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735919160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fcbjhjd3o_supreme-court-of-india_62