ure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Singh%20found%20that%20the%20root%20case%20of%20addictions%20lie%20in%20certain%20experiences%20that%20the%20person%20has%20battled.%20Through%20a%20holistic%20treatment%20plan%2C%20they%20are%20helped%20get%20back%20on%20track%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fdrug-de-addiction-Rajinder-Singh-7-1734944123-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391707%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESingh%20found%20that%20the%20root%20case%20of%20addictions%20lies%20in%20certain%20experiences%20that%20the%20person%20has%20battled.%20Through%20a%20holistic%20treatment%20plan%2C%20they%20are%20helped%20get%20back%20on%20track%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20goal%20of%20rehabilitation%20is%20moral%20reckoning.%20It%20is%20only%20after%20this%2C%20that%20transformation%20can%20begin.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20tells%20the%20story%20of%2032-year-old%20Deepak%20(%3Cem%3Ename%20changed%20on%20request%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20who%20was%20admitted%20for%20a%20nine-year%20history%20of%20using%20intravenous%20injections%20of%20Norphin%20