0they%20would%20find%20some%20work%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20we%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20forest%20and%20the%20goodwill%20of%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9COur%20village%20was%20a%20small%20settlement%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20forest.%20Because%20of%20the%20forest%20animals%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20cultivate%20any%20food%20for%20ourselves%3B%20as%20they%20would%20destroy%20the%20crops.%20We%20only%20had%20two%20choices%3A%20either%20become%20a%20labourer%20or%20head%20into%20the%20jungle%20to%20collect%20wild%20potatoes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20there%20was%20no%20concept%20of%20a%20market%2C%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20family%20had%20to%20ask%20the%20landowners%20or%20wealthier%20people%20for%20rice%3B%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%E2%80%99d%20eat.%20I%20grew%20up%20eating%20that%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEager%20to%20learn%2C%20he%20overcame%20several%20challenges%20to%20attend%20night%20school%20but%20had%20to%20discontinue%20after%20class%205.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20survival%20had%20taken%20precedence%2C%20and%20Sarbeswar%20took%20up%20a%20job%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267799%2Fnit-karnataka-electric-bike-forest-surveillance-kudremukh-battery-range-specs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20forest%20guard%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20office%3B%20here%2C%20he%20spent%20about%20a%20year%2C%20taking%20care%20of%20poultry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201561px)%20100vw%2C%201561px%