20saw%20the%20lioness%20spring.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20pure%20mayhem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20moment%2C%20Mumbai-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366242%2Fshreyovi-mehta-shivang-mehta-wildlife-photographer-nature-wanderers-natural-history-museum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20photographer%3C%2Fa%3E%20Parag%20Bhatt%20says%20that%20the%20lioness%20inching%20closer%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20cousin%E2%80%99s%20frantic%20urges%20to%20usher%20him%20into%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20later%2C%20when%20he%20was%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20(figuratively%20and%20metaphorically)%2C%20that%20the%20dread%20ebbed%2C%20leaving%20him%20with%20an%20aftertaste%20of%20ambition.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20wildlife%20photographer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParag%20credits%20his%20aptitude%20for%20the%20wild%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Kenya.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20would%20often%20tell%20me%20stories%20of%20how%20the%20animals%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20caged%20but%20roamed%20free.%E2%80%9D%20His%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephotographic%20acumen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20comes%20from%20his%20father%2C%20who%20was%20a%20photographer.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20young%20boy%2C%20I%20remember%20assisting%20him%20