n-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-2-1734543257-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390690%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rescue%20mission%20is%20done%20where%20multiple%20Government%20departments%20are%20involved.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20SOP%20demands%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20rescue%20mission%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20departments%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20SDM%20sometimes%20delays%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shekhar%20admits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20are%20the%20facilitators%20for%20the%20rescue%20mission%2C%20we%20become%20the%20witness%20for%20the%20same.%20The%20Government%20deals%20with%20proper%20documentation%20of%20the%20details.%20All%20the%20FIR%20copies%20are%20maintained%20by%20us%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20the%20conducted%20and%20upcoming%20missions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20date%20and%20time%20for%20the%20rescue%20mission%20are%20fixed%20without%20revealing%20details%20like%20the%20address%20and%20factory%20name%20to%20avoid%20external%20hurdles%20and%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20political%20pressure%20and%20involvement%20of%20goons%20makes%20the%20res